# Docker Sample App

This is a simple Flask application that runs in a Docker container. It provides a fun fortune-telling feature.

## How to run

1. Pull the image:
   ```
   docker pull pqrpqr/docker-sample-app:latest
   ```

2. Run the container:
   ```
   docker run -p 5000:5000 pqrpqr/docker-sample-app:latest
   ```

3. Access the application at `http://localhost:5000`

Enjoy your fortune!
